title: Skateboarding - Another_Day - Sun Diego Boardshop
description:
Sun Diego's 2nd skate video Another Day. 2005.  San Diego skateboarders and homies.
  
Featuring: greg lutzka, rodney jones, brandon turner, dallas rockvam, steve mcneal, tyler surrey, wes kremer, alex perelson, marius syvanen, steve shipler, james mcknight, gabe ryan (gyeah!), matt kriegel, truman hooker, kashawn jackson, steve roche, trung gno, and more.
